# Title: Suspicious Execution Location Of Wermgr.EXE
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-10-14
# Level: high
# Description: Detects suspicious Windows Error Reporting manager (wermgr.exe) execution location.
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wermgr_susp_exec_location.yml

Image="*\\wermgr.exe" NOT (Image IN ("C:\\Windows\\System32\\*", "C:\\Windows\\SysWOW64\\*", "C:\\Windows\\WinSxS\\*"))